#### **실무 영향 예시 (AIOps 5단계 붕괴 시나리오)**

```
【 Scenario: Reconnecting RMC + Delayed RCA Poisoning 조합 】

Day 1-5: Normal operations
  - Alert precision: 95%
  - RCA accuracy: 90%
  - MTTR: 30 min

Day 6: First RMC attack (label-flipping 20%)
  - Detected & quarantined (우리 detector에 의해)
  - But without DPoS quarantine, reconnect 쉬움

Day 10: RMC reconnects + RCA task delay-poisoning starts
  - Alert precision: 95% → 65% (FP ↑)
  - RCA accuracy: 90% → 60% (cross-task propagation)
  - 운영팀: "뭔가 이상한데..."

Day 15: Adaptive magnitude attack evolution
  - Alert precision: 65% → 35% (fatigue 심화)
  - RCA: 60% → 40% (cascading cascading...)
  - Critical incident missed: $50K loss

Day 20: Collusion network 형성 + 3개 reconnnect sybil
  - f: 20% → 45% (effective Byzantine)
  - 모든 task: degradation
  - System 신뢰 붕괴: 운영팀 자동화 무시

Cost: $200K alert fatigue + $300K wrong RCA remediation + $100K manual response
     = $600K+ per week if not stopped
```

이 5가지 공격 유형은 모두 **기존 aggregation-only defense로는 불가능**하고, **우리의 3가지 기여 (trajectory detection + task-aware aggregation + DPoS quarantine)로만 대응 가능**합니다.

